pages.text: 0 Here. there. anywhere really. king does it all. Have a group of 20 looking for Golden Hour cocktails and snacks? Or a boisterous 120 looking for the perfect place to celebrate your favorite couple and hang your hats for the evening? Or do you have the “where” taken care of, now all you need are some delicious, delicious ribs... On site or off, King can bring the party to you. Just sit back, relax, and let us take care of the good food and vibes part, leaving you to make the good times and memories. Just need some ? Easy peasy, we can do that, too. pick up catering
